data.description: Desirable North Long BEACH location with low maintenance and DEEDED BEACH ACCESS! This open and airy Condo with Main Level Primary Bedroom, that leads out to spacious Backyard and covered Patio area, is just a short walk to the BEACH! Open Kitchen/Dining/Living Area opens up to Trex Deck and Side Yard to enjoy wildlife and afternoon sun! Upper Level has it's own Primary Bedroom, Loft and Bonus Room for extra storage! Take a short stroll to the Discovery Trail or Golf Course and just minutes to Downtown Long BEACH for Shopping, Restaurants, Festivals and Fun!
